HOTS
====

Setup
-----

Install mongrel2, zeromq, py-zmq, skytools 3

Testing
-------
- Create confdb with sql/apiwrapper.sql
- Put confdb location into conf/hots-dbsrv.ini

- configure paths in ./startweb.sh
- launch ./startweb.sh
- connect with browser to localhost:4080

Current plumbing
----------------

scripts/tasks:
- remote-pub / to cc-logging-sub
- remote-req / to cc-db-req

cc: per-host controller
- remote-pub / to logsrv-sub
- remote-req / to dbsrv-rep
- local-sub / logging proxy
- local-rep / confdb proxy

logsrv: zmq log destination
- local-sub / waits for remote log
- local-pub / log re-publish
- logdb / db connection to logdb

dbsrv/confdb: zmq <> confdb proxy
- local-rep / replies for confdb requests
- confdb / db connection to confdb

mongrel2: http <> zmq proxy
- local-pub / http req
- local-sub / http replies

websrv:
- remote-sub: logsrv-pub
- remote-req: confdb-rep
- remote-sub: mongrel-pub
- remote-pub: mongrel-sub


